metadata.name: Jump into a New BAR
metadata.description:
新しい世界に飛び込むには少しの勇気がいる。
それでも、一歩踏み出せば、広がる景色は無限の可能性と光に満ちた世界。
イベントにてCryptoで支払える新しいBARを開いた時のイメージから着想しました。

It takes a little courage to jump into a new world.
Yet, once you take the first step, the view that opens up is a world filled with infinite possibilities and light.
It was inspired by the image of a new bar that opened at an event where people could pay in cryptocurrency.
